{"word":"Samuel","slug":"samuel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Samuel</b> - son of Elkanah and Hannah, the last of the Judges,<p/>General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=20'>1Sa 1:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=11'>1Sa 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=18'>1Sa 2:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=3&verse=1'>1Sa 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=3&verse=19'>1Sa 3:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=4&verse=1'>1Sa 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=15'>1Sa 7:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=8&verse=1'>1Sa 8:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=9&verse=14'>1Sa 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=11'>1Sa 13:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=1'>1Sa 16:1</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=19&verse=18'>1Sa 19:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25&verse=1'>1Sa 25:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=28&verse=3'>1Sa 28:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=28&verse=11'>1Sa 28:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=22'>1Ch 9:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=99&verse=6'>Psa 99:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=15&verse=1'>Jer 15:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=32'>Heb 11:32</a><p/>---\"The Upright Judge\"<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=12&verse=3'>1Sa 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=12&verse=4'>1Sa 12:4</a><p/>Life Summarized<p/>Consecrated to God by his parents<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=24'>1Sa 1:24-28</a><p/>A wonderful childhood<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=8'>1Sa 2:8-21</a><p/>--like that of Christ<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=26'>1Sa 2:26</a><p/>--Heard God's voice in boyhood<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=3&verse=1'>1Sa 3:1-18</a><p/>--Courageous<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=13'>1Sa 13:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=15&verse=16'>1Sa 15:16-29</a><p/>A man of prayer<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=5'>1Sa 7:5-8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=8&verse=6'>1Sa 8:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=12&verse=17'>1Sa 12:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=15&verse=11'>1Sa 15:11</a><p/>An Inspired prophet<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=3&verse=19'>1Sa 3:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=3&verse=21'>1Sa 3:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=8&verse=22'>1Sa 8:22</a><p/>A circuit judge<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=16'>1Sa 7:16</a>"}]}